							<span class="comment_author">Jeanne</span>
							<span class="comment_date">February 15, 2026</span>
							<div class="comment_text" id="comment-body-771220">
<p>I made your tahini today and then decided to make the hummus. Both are perfect! I added a little Calabrian hot chili powder to the hummus and sprinkled more on top with some smoked paprika. Topped with a little chopped parsley for extra color. Both are fantastic recipes. My husband had a hard time putting the hummus away. Needless to say, I just ordered 5 lbs. of sesame seeds. I wonder what I&#8217;ll use those for ;). Thank you!</p>
<div class="itr_rating-comment"><span class="itr-rate-stars"></p>
<div class="itr-rating-comment-inner"><span class="rated"><svg viewBox="0 0 22 22" height="18" width="18" class="rated"><polygon points="9.9, 1.1, 3.3, 21.78, 19.8, 8.58, 0, 8.58, 16.5, 21.78" style="fill-rule:nonzero;"></polygon></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 22 22" height="18" width="18" class="rated"><polygon points="9.9, 1.1, 3.3, 21.78, 19.8, 8.58, 0, 8.58, 16.5, 21.78" style="fill-rule:nonzero;"></polygon></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 22 22" height="18" width="18" class="rated"><polygon points="9.9, 1.1, 3.3, 21.78, 19.8, 8.58, 0, 8.58, 16.5, 21.78" style="fill-rule:nonzero;"></polygon></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 22 22" height="18" width="18" class="rated"><polygon points="9.9, 1.1, 3.3, 21.78, 19.8, 8.58, 0, 8.58, 16.5, 21.78" style="fill-rule:nonzero;"></polygon></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 22 22" height="18" width="18" class="rated"><polygon points="9.9, 1.1, 3.3, 21.78, 19.8, 8.58, 0, 8.58, 16.5, 21.78" style="fill-rule:nonzero;"></polygon></svg></span></div>
